Sentence: ['Oh, my god, I am so glad you called me. I had the most supremely awful day.', "We got the proofs back from that photo shoot, you know, the one with the little vegetables. So if you want, I have a bag with just your heads.', 'Oh, are you sure? Really? Because you know, you could make little puppets out of them, and you could use them in your theater of cruelty.', 'Just us.', "Although, I have enjoyed the fact that, uh your shirt's been stickin' outta your zipper ever since you came back from the bathroom. ", 'So, do we have the best friends or what?', 'I will go for that drink.', 'Each.', "Happy Valentine's Day!", 'Oh, I miss you already. Can you believe this happened?', 'Kiss me!', 'Hi, Monica.', 'This is so fun. This is like a reunion in the hall.', "Hi, Ross. Yes, it's me. How did you know?  ", 'Hello, funny Valentine.', "Hello, Joey, our little matchmaker. I could just kiss you all over, and I'm gonna!", 'I brought you something.', 'I had them made special.', "That's fine.", "Mmm-hmm. Because I know that this isn't the end.", "No, it isn't, because you won't let that happen. Don't you know it yet? You love me, Chandler Bing.", "Well then ask yourself this. Why do you think we keep ending up together? New Year's? Who invited who? Valentine's? Who asked who into whose bed? ", "You seek me out. Something deep in your soul calls out to me like a foghorn. Janice, Janice. You want me. You need me. You can't live without me. And you know it. You just don't know you know it. See ya.", 'Oh, my, god.', 'Helloo!!', "Hey, it's everybody.", 'Yes, I am.', 'Is it yours? Ha! You wish, Chandler Bing. You are looking at a married lady now.', "Oh, sweetie, I'm sorry.", 'And what? Missed the expression on your face? Janice likes to have her fun.', 'Oh, I wish. Look, honey, you have that report to finish, and I gotta go see my lawyer. ', ' I-I-I gotta go, I gotta go. So, this is my idea: you and me spending some quality time together.", 'For Chandler!', "Okay. All right. This is what we're gonna call it: 'Joey and Janice's DAY OF FUN!'", "Yes, because that's how long it takes to love me.", "We're baack!", "Joey and Janice's DAY OF FUN!!! ", "I just came by to give you a kiss, I have to go pick up the baby, so. I'll see you later sweetheart, you too Chandler. ", 'Night-night Bing-a-ling.', 'Oh. God, crazy Chandler. He spun me...off...the...bed!', "Oh,  I wish. No, you know he was just trying Ross's Hug and Roll thing. ", 'You know what, where he hugs you and kinda rolls you away and... Oh... my....God.', "Well, let's go to a bad one and make out. ", 'What is the great tragedy here? God.', 'How are you Ms. Hot Shot chef with the big fancy restaurant with the best chicken ever! ', ' Ohh! What is that on your finger?! Im blind!', 'So, whos the lucky guy?', 'Oh. I was wondering if I could maybe stay here with you, just I really feel that I need to be with family.', 'Please, its because otherwise I really dont know what I might do.', ' Do you have any tissues?', 'Okay!
